  "observable_contract": [
    {
      "contract": "When `rstb` is below `vth`, clear both PFD states and hold both outputs low. While `rstb` is high, a rising crossing of `ref` asserts `up`, and a rising crossing of `fb` asserts `down`. Once both states have occurred, schedule a reset after `reset_delay` and clear both states at that timer event. The reset input must also clear a pending one-sided UP or DOWN state even if the opposite edge has not arrived.",
      "property_id": "P_WHEN_RSTB_IS_BELOW_VTH_CLEAR",
      "required_signals": [
        "time",
        "down",
        "fb",
        "ref",
        "rstb",
        "up"
      ]
    },
    {
      "contract": "`vth = 0.45 V`: threshold for `ref`, `fb`, and `rstb`.",
      "property_id": "P_VTH_0_45_V_THRESHOLD_FOR",
      "required_signals": [
        "time",
        "down",
        "fb",
        "ref",
        "rstb",
        "up"
      ]
    },
    {
      "contract": "`vh = 0.9 V`: logic-high output level.",
      "property_id": "P_VH_0_9_V_LOGIC_HIGH",
      "required_signals": [
        "time",
        "down",
        "fb",
        "ref",
        "rstb",
        "up"
      ]
    },
    {
      "contract": "`reset_delay = 80 ps from [0:inf)`: delay from the moment both detector states are asserted to the mutual reset event.",
      "property_id": "P_RESET_DELAY_80_PS_FROM_0",
      "required_signals": [
        "time",
        "down",
        "fb",
        "ref",
        "rstb",
        "up"
      ]
    },
    {
      "contract": "`tr = 10 ps from [0:inf)`: output transition smoothing time.",
      "property_id": "P_TR_10_PS_FROM_0_INF",
      "required_signals": [
        "time",
        "down",
        "fb",
        "ref",
        "rstb",
        "up"
      ]
    },
    {
      "contract": "- `vth = 0.45 V`: threshold for `ref`, `fb`, and `rstb`. - `vh = 0.9 V`: logic-high output level. - `reset_delay = 80 ps from [0:inf)`: delay from the moment both detector states are asserted to the mutual reset event. - `tr = 10 ps from [0:inf)`: output transition smoothing time.",
